            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "港股跌勢喘定 暫於22900點上下徘徊",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美國關稅細節拖累全球股市氣氛，港股今早跟隨外圍大幅低開後，於早市中段跌勢已暫見喘定。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240806_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240806_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">截至上午約10時40分，恒生指數報22914點，跌287點或1.24%；今早最低曾見22638點，挫564點，最高曾挑戰二萬三關口，一度衝上22998點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數報5333點，跌93點或1.71%。出口相關股壓力較明顯，申洲國際(02313)跌約15%，是表現最佳藍籌；創科實業(00669)也跌近9%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"申洲國際官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1119x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/02313_WEB_1200.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"申洲國際官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1119x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/02313_WEB_1200.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">申洲國際官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">連續兩日在藍籌表現包尾的小米(01810)，今早逆市反彈，暫升約2%；中芯(00981)也升約1.8%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14827000-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e8%b7%8c%e5%8b%a2%e5%96%98%e5%ae%9a-%e6%9a%ab%e6%96%bc22900%e9%bb%9e%e4%b8%8a%e4%b8%8b%e5%be%98%e5%be%8a",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240415_FI_source-web_HKStock-3.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-03 10:50:39",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
